title: Production, casting heat up on Lee Daniels' TV pilot 'Star'
text: > Entertainment Production, casting heat up on Lee Daniels' TV pilot 'Star' FILE - In this Aug. 6, 2015 file photo, Lee Daniels attends the 2015 Summer TCA - Fox All-Star Party at Soho House in Los Angeles. Production will begin in December 2015 on "Star," a drama pilot from "Empire" creator Daniels. Fox, which airs "Empire" and ordered the "Star" pilot, also said that an online casting search is under way for the drama. (Photo by Paul A. Hebert/Invision/AP, File)
